{"tid":1305101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者、議員、律師唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T12:42:27.000Z","uid":112748,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"db7e8e4a7b650bfc68ea832f9a1909c0002776f1","tid":1305101,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:59:26.000Z","msg":"大家都有眼見！近呢幾日開始關於各區連儂牆，啲學生年青人開始被班惡型惡相既人，挑釁，或者係襲擊  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/918257375180106/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fvideos%2F918257375180106%2F&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=736d53cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/videos/918257375180106/</a><br />\n唔該可唔可以提供一個保護到呢班學生、年青人街頭上既保護到自已人生安全既意見？<br />\n呢個唔關乎政見問題，係人生安全問題，有大量網民開始唔再相信警方會公正執法，醞釀緊以暴抑暴去面對街頭上遇到的真正&quot;暴民&quot;，究竟可唔可以做一次專題，提供有利既法律意見，還唔還手好？唔還手係咪對方會受罰重d？兩邊都有郁手既拳腳交都係和解？有流血無流血嚴重性唔同d？用武器既傷害先會罰重d？<br />\n教下呢班年青人，點樣避免跌落牢獄陷阱、點樣搜証、清清楚楚既處理方法？因為我唔想再見到呢班後生仔女，不斷....不斷被人襲擊，唔該！"},{"pid":"91ddc98bbd72aef60c63009fe94ab572fa987034","tid":1305101,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96877c02c69dd995016b815e228536f7a7179d1b","tid":1305101,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d01c6fd65da04c33ebd3f041ffb7455777ba2e9","tid":1305101,"uid":99122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:01:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6b4487744230d50cfa41dd3c78ba1ca10fa208c0","tid":1305101,"uid":256316,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:02:04.000Z","msg":"唔好推"},{"pid":"5b81faf1